 or brocade, or sitting upon anything made from them. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5499,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2067 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37473,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/05\/wonders-of-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":15295,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Wonders of Paradise for the believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 5, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Qays reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, in Paradise is a tent made of a hollowed pearl sixty miles wide, in each corner are families who do not see each other. The believers will roam freely between them. There are two\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15415,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/prophet-seven-commands\/","url_meta":{"origin":15295,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ahkam: Seven prohibitions and commands","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara' ibn 'Azib reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, prohibited us from seven things: using gold rings, silk, flax, brocade, red saddle clothes, taffeta, and silver vessels. And the Prophet commanded us to do seven things: to visit the sick, to follow the funeral procession, to bless\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3791,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/24\/muslim-who-fasts-distant-hellfire\/","url_meta":{"origin":15295,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: A Muslim who fasts will be distant from Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\"Whoever fasts a day in the way of Allah, Allah will move his face away from the Hellfire by a distance of seventy years.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2840, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1153 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31579,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/31\/people-mines-silver-gold\/","url_meta":{"origin":15295,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Fiqh: People like mines of silver and gold","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 31, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPeople are like minerals of silver and gold. The best of them in the time of ignorance are the best of them in Islam, if they have religious understanding.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2638 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdo